<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Rutland" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Rutland,</orth> 1) the earldom granted to Edward Aumerle, after he was deprived of his dukedom: <bibl n="shak. r2 5.2.43" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 2, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.96" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 96</bibl>. 2) son of Richard Duke of York, slain by Clifford: <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 78</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 78</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.63" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 63</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.158" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 158</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.178" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 178</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.45" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.45" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 45</bibl>
